    "With respect to the metaverse in education, computational problems are presented by the real-time collection and processing of interactive data between the virtual and physical worlds (Zhou, 2022).",
    "Furthermore, the information security of instructors, students, and others cannot be entirely assured.",
    "In addition, there is a greater chance of personal privacy leakage.",
    "It is also claimed that using anonymous logins may pose concerns and lead to violations.",
    "According to Zhang et al. (2022), owing to a greater degree of online anonymity in the metaverse, it will be easier for students with narrow social experiences to be subjected to criminal activities such as fraud, spying, and leaks."
